testcase.name: ClientStorageModule Storage Factory `storageServiceFactory` should create factory for Storage Service
StorageService should be created with provided configuration
StorageService should throw `TypeError` if a new value is assigned to a readonly property
StorageService should be able to save in session storage with encryption
StorageService should be able to save in session storage without encryption
StorageService should be able to fetch data from session storage
StorageService should be able to clear session storage via clear() method
StorageService Utility method _getTrueValue should return value with true type
StorageService Utility method _parseJSON should return parsed javaScript object or false
